OL,14,Fallegations concerning the
OL,15,Fdirector-general in January, which was
OL,16,Flooked into and dealt with "in line
OL,17,Fwith CBI procedure". It had "determined
OL,18,Fthat the issue did not require
OL,19,Fescalation to a disciplinary process".
